=== Etymology ===

From [[ימן]] {{HH|3231}}; 
=== Noun ===
the right hand or side (leg, eye) of a person or other object (as the stronger and more dexterous); locally, the south: -  + left-handed, right (hand, side), south.
[[fr:ימין]]